<p>She said: 'I’m happy being single at the moment. I’m just enjoying myself. I’m having fun. I don’t kiss and tell but it is nice.' </p>

<p>The blonde bombshell also blamed their 'busy schedules' for pulling them apart from each other. </p>

<p>She confessed: 'We were just better off as friends…we had such busy schedules and we both realised that it was better to break it off now and we could still be friends.</p>

<p>The former couple's relationship appeared to be on the rocks when fans noticed they were sat apart from one another at the Love Island final. </p>
